sources.title: Enchanted | Full Movie | Romantic Comedy | Sydney Penny | Happy Valentine's
sources.description:
Enchanted - When it comes to giving advice, David Russell had the answers for his close group of college friends. But when it came to his own life, David is lost in the world of Hollywood fantasies and dreams.
1998.  Stars: John Ward, Sydney Penny, David Kaufman
